306
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:39,260
I think you'll understand my choice.

307
00:25:44,040 --> 00:25:44,940
I do.

308
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:48,850
When the job is done,

309
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:51,570
drop by home and see us.

310
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:52,700
I will.

311
00:25:54,280 --> 00:25:55,980
By then, I believe,

312
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:57,530
