is the Nationalist Army 405th Battalion.

344
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:39,700
So as long as the 405th Battalion

345
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,020
triggers the air raid siren

346
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:42,940
after the telegram is sent,

347
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:43,570
then,

348
00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:45,180
to the Japanese,

