365
00:28:53,390 --> 00:28:53,980
Mr. Cao,

366
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:55,500
as far as I know,

367
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:58,500
the Commander-in-Chief
of Su-Lu-Wan Border,

368
00:28:59,000 --> 00:28:59,850
Li Mingyang,

