376
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,260
Mr. Cao,

377
00:29:25,110 --> 00:29:28,090
for you, it's just a phone call,

378
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:30,570
but for the people in Northern Jiangsu,

379
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,020
it's a matter of life and death.

380
00:29:40,870 --> 00:29:41,980
Commissioner Luo.

381
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:44,060
Do you think he's just messing around?

382
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:44,850
It's worth a try.

383
00:29:47,150 --> 00:29:48,060
It's worth a try.

