389
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,060
I didn't.

390
00:29:58,560 --> 00:30:00,980
Honestly, I still think this is risky.

391
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:02,410
But,

392
00:30:03,590 --> 00:30:04,540
if it works,

393
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:05,980
