I just wanted to test your resolve.

398
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,130
Alright, I'm in.

399
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,220
As for Chief Commander Li,

400
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:31,020
I'll go talk to him myself.

401
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:32,300
Well,

402
00:30:32,630 --> 00:30:34,740
