442
00:35:31,880 --> 00:35:33,820
If you don't want to go, why agree?

443
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:41,650
Him?

444
00:35:41,790 --> 00:35:46,210
He's a spoiled heir from the Gu family.

445
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,690
Really naive.

446
00:35:49,790 --> 00:35:51,860
If I turn him down to his face,

447
00:35:53,270 --> 00:35:54,460
