450
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:05,290
If he wants to act, I'll play along.

451
00:36:05,310 --> 00:36:07,690
But if he's heading into danger,

452
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:10,820
I won't go that far for him.

453
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,060
After all, I have family to care for.

454
00:36:13,560 --> 00:36:14,060
Come in.

455
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:17,940
Mr. Cao, the car's ready.

456
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,690
Alright, I'm on my way.

457
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,340
If he asks about it later,

458
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:28,290
