00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:43,130
Tell them to prep for an air raid.

465
00:36:43,750 --> 00:36:44,500
At eight o'clock sharp,

466
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:46,980
you'll have the nearest 405th Battalion

467
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,290
