00:38:59,150 --> 00:39:00,460
I'll head to the Bureau first.

509
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:02,980
Wait, why are you going there?

510
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,130
Seriously, at this hour?

511
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,700
Before you even arrive there,

512
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:08,610
